songs.title: Triple Helix
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from snippet

Back in 1-7 could never imagine embeddin' the bezel with VVS stones (Yeah)
Miami 11, I walk through the section, like Malcolm in middle, got three different hoes (Yeah)
Pourin' up like a alchemist, mix it up, get high, I escape my lows (Yeah)
Pourin' up like a alchemist, mix it up, get high, I escape my lows (Yeah, what?)
No, I can't ever love a cop, they got my pops and it made me watch (No)
Told bro, "Don't move with the mop," might clean up the block like he missed a spot (Oh yeah)
I wasn't worth a lot (Yeah), I had to raise my-
